# Assets Exposures Total Amount

## identifier
de14098

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of total exposure. Exposure represents the purchase of a financial product or other item of value with an expectation of favourable future returns.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Exposures.Total.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.15
- period=instant
